{"tid":661669,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"徐腎 水原希子 戶田 生田斗真 大野智 慘被改做死人相 😱","createTime":"2018-05-11T18:47:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T08:43:50.000Z","uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0d046cb43f97f68aee21508a50a8c460ea116a24","tid":661669,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T18:47:19.000Z","msg":"支那節目咁仆街 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/12/022703_d7d9f2b73d239455753dc2c9128368a9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F12%2F022703_d7d9f2b73d239455753dc2c9128368a9.png&h=4f18cbb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2I8lf1v\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2I8lf1v&d=tZQ2PVDpD6vOu9q9%2BN92c%2BargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=06bd192a\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2I8lf1v</a>"},{"pid":"f411d4422b5a8a0108cddfbc8bd3797bc266a70b","tid":661669,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T18:47:55.000Z","msg":"少女時代徐玄（又譯：徐賢）慘被改圖做遺照？話說大陸芒果TV綜藝節目《密室逃脱‧暗夜古宅》，由唐禹哲和黄宥明等內地明星參與演出，開播時已在國內掀起一陣熱話。最近播出的一集《密室逃脱‧暗夜古宅》，卻因為採用了國外藝人的照片，來合成遺照而引起網民激烈批評！多位藝人慘遭利用，其中竟包括Kpop天團少女時代徐玄！雖然該集《密室逃脱‧暗夜古宅》現在已經下架，但依然未能平息SONE（少女時代粉絲）的怒火！"},{"pid":"59ab8d4d4c6672e808b4d8929f42450e9059c983","tid":661669,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T18:48:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2rByRHv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2rByRHv&d=tZQ2PVDpD6vOu9q9%2BN92c%2BargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=86a17b44\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2rByRHv</a><br />\n中國綜藝節目《密室逃脱‧暗夜古宅》的1張遺照線索中，驚現少女時代徐玄改圖"},{"pid":"f7f8a4cba0eae653d864282a6fe89023ed653ca1","tid":661669,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T18:50:07.000Z","msg":"《密室逃脱‧暗夜古宅》最近一集中的其中一個線索，為8個人的遺照。眼利的觀眾當場發現，遺照是由多位國外藝人的照片，經合成和改圖而成。中國SONE首先發現少女時代徐玄的高中學生照，慘被惡意黑白化和改圖用於恐怖血腥的場景。除了少女時代徐玄外，慘被改圖的更包括：水原希子、戶田惠梨香、生田斗真和大野智等日本藝人。少女時代「徐賢中國應援會」表示，芒果TV未經本人許可，就擅自改圖成遺像，絕對違背人倫道德常理！而且在未經少女時代徐玄同意下擅自將合成圖醜化，並在媒體中傳播，更加是無視藝人肖像權與尊嚴！"},{"pid":"70fd36c6a22785550744c0b5a9c2ae2489c9a5e3","tid":661669,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T18:51:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2G9V2cW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2G9V2cW&d=tZQ2PVDpD6vOu9q9%2BN92c%2BargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=d9e07edb\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2G9V2cW</a><br />\n<br />\n有中國SONE對比《密室逃脱‧暗夜古宅》的「遺照」和少女時代徐玄學生照的原圖，不能否認節目組是使用了她的學生照改圖。"},{"pid":"7e96aeb4db9b3313bed76b1d995fc05b082e09b3","tid":661669,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T18:56:08.000Z","msg":"製作單位也急忙出面澄清，聲稱「道具是用智能軟件，隨機抓曲全網素材智能合成的，而後將合成出的照片進行最後一道PS工序最終輸出，絕無故意與惡意指向任何真實人物形象」，此集內容也已刪除，待重新剪輯再上架。"},{"pid":"bf362c91208338989949cea4508a1cfb6a718abd","tid":661669,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T19:02:35.000Z","msg":"淨係認得出徐腎嗰張，其他人唔似既<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/14/105309_dc4d89861da876a3fb8154d45d96f0b1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F14%2F105309_dc4d89861da876a3fb8154d45d96f0b1.png&h=696d470f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c110bcc102c2b8832a9b4dffa61f7bcf53db089","tid":661669,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T19:26:18.000Z","msg":"冇片冇偈傾？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png&h=e2c59df6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9da76ee1929ea8e0f3970f78f3f1355a8af6ee7c","tid":661669,"uid":70988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c110bcc102c2b8832a9b4dffa61f7bcf53db089","tid":661669,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":